
FitHub is used for source code management system.

In azure we use Azure Repos as SCM.

VCM : In github, git is used as Version control Management.

we need to add each file to git so that it can track every thing regarding that file.

git status is used to cheack weather the files are added into git or not.

if the files are not added to git then it will show the files in Red color including some msg.




We use git commnads for the code changes
git clone github    // clone means copy

cd repository

git add

git commit

git push

git pull
